node.title: Man arrested and charged with murder of 10-month-old baby
node.description: The baby was rushed to hospital after sustaining what police believe were non-accidental injuries.
node.content: ["Police have arrested and charged a 21-year-old man with murder following the death of 10-month-old baby Chance Kamanaka O Ke Akura Aipolani-Nielson.\u00a0", "Chance died in Starship Hospital last Friday after sustaining what police believe to be non-accidental injuries.\u00a0", "The 21-year-old man is expected to appear in the North Shore District Court tomorrow.\u00a0", "Waitemat\u0101 Detective Inspector Aaron Proctor said police's sympathies are with Chance's wh\u0101nau at this extremely difficult and tragic time.", "As this matter is now before the Courts, police are unable to comment further.\u00a0", "\u00a0"]
